top.value: CEECFOODS is a network on food composition for Central and Eastern European countries. The activities of the Food Research Institute under theMinistry of Agriculture areaimed at buildingcapacities and technical support of food databases in selected countries of Central and Eastern Europe, like Moldova, Macedonia, Montenegro, Albania.

FAO CEECFOODS je projekt Vskumnho stavu potravinrskeho zameran na odborn a technick podporu krajn SVE v oblasti potravinovch databz. Sstreuje sa na 3 oblasti - budovanie kapact, podpora vzdelvania a vvoj softvru pre vybran krajiny SVE (Moldavsko, Macednsko, ierna Hora, Bosna a Hercegovina, Albnsko).
